Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==========正文==========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開玲子的遺物做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.56,0:01:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  倒不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.33,0:01:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.00,0:01:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺  一如既往地讓人搞不懂的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.61,0:01:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西瓜籽  嘴兩邊  兩粒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意  不知不覺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次還給妖怪名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子的記憶成為思念  注入我的內心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:16.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子這個人  一點點地…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.60,0:02:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向圖書館借的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是忘記還了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車票？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得是哪方錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙說油炸豆腐清湯麵裡的豆腐是先吃的  難以置信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是先吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐是要浸在湯汁裡最後吃的  是吧夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  豆腐是要趁甜味沒有被湯汁沖淡前吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…我是覺得怎麼都可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐要後吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豆腐要先吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼爭論之前  那個不叫豆腐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是後吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先吃對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.92,0:03:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  正和我意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:39.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊的爭吵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  你掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以前的車票吧  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟夏目有什麼關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼說道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣…今早上學時撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拙劣的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.19,0:04:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會再好好問你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃也沒用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡…回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要去那張車票的站頭吧  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車站在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才沒看清楚  忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在附近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹田  你為什麼這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  自上次的試膽大會以來  我真的想見個面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見誰  你真討厭  這不明擺著的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  車來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.33,0:04:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你掉東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:04:57.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.18,0:05:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒掉東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  到底我掉了什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:27.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算來了嗎  真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經不使用了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像很久之前就成為廢線了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.72,0:06:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真淒涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧沼是在另一邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過為什麼玲子又…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼熱還真虧它能睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玲子  終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:41.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是玲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不是玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  想點辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說什麼都沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼壞東西  你就陪他玩一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  玲子死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是孫子嘛  氣味相似也不足為奇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.70,0:07:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用聞得這麼細緻入微
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  濃毛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說在這裡等玲子  是不是有什麼約定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  她說會和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.59,0:07:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧沼  玲子要和你一起去霧沼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  霧沼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.59,0:07:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗡嗡地叫  說「不會原諒你的」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是玲子就說「不行啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:07.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這傢伙來說明還真是為難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.20,0:08:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許這傢伙在友人帳上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把名字還給它的話  思念會傳達給我們事由的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字  我叫三都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.67,0:08:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾之守護喲  昭顯其名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.09,0:08:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣的是實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡那個叫實栗的妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡實栗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:09:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是實栗說討厭我  不想再見我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做錯什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.60,0:09:08.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那實栗對你說了什麼生氣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.13,0:09:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像多少有點明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗生氣的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊  玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗現在在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧沼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧沼  鄰站的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  那我和你一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.46,0:09:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天天色已晚  明天再在此碰頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很癢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.95,0:09:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  沒能完成約定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是玲子有了什麼不能來的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方可能已經不在等待了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去一下是不會知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.27,0:10:26.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去  要完成玲子沒做完的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.43,0:10:31.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過今天天色已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天放學後我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了  還是現在就動身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  輕易就答應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧沼附近可沒有公交車通過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道走過去要多久嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那肯定天都黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是白說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子不來的話  你一個人不也可以去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就這麼傻等著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為約好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻  居然去問他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.11,0:11:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始變冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像山間的寒風在流入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說這傢伙是可愛呢還是煩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到實栗的話  準備怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  沒想過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.93,0:12:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和好的話  得說點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是別讓他們見面比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許反而會變麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都  在到達之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想好要說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨念？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會原諒  不會原諒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓穩囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是三都
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來實栗被地靈附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被地靈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為地靈喜好憤怒及仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗對三都如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.42,0:13:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不要去見對方為好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得怎樣我都不管了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啊  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊  仿佛不是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是山間的寒風
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怨念所致吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.38,0:14:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗  出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗  有話要跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都  實栗長什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:55.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…小小的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的  是多小
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是開玩笑的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼在  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鯰…鯰魚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那就是實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分明是奇大無比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.99,0:16:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦夏目  要說服它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.21,0:16:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子  是夏目玲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好  把友人帳交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳在那裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是玲子的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.18,0:17:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗  實栗  是我  三都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好  快醒過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.16,0:17:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗  快回來  求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帳給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不給
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.62,0:17:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:49.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:59.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很可憐  看來跟地靈一起消失在沼澤底了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  到底搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  三都你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要做什麼笨蛋  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣  很噁心啊  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說放開我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.78,0:18:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  吵架是因為玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因為夏目玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這蠢貨把重要的名字給了玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:51.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有作為妖怪的自尊嗎  你這大蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來再也不想見你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻又恬不知恥地出現了  你這呆瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  不用這麼說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三都喜歡你  所以一直牽掛著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說它蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心道歉的話給我快點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:11.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.48,0:19:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  實栗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  看仔細了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  有在聽嗎濃毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個傢伙  早就和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實栗  我們回山裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說也會回去的  你個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  真的謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  別向人類低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  他把名字也還給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.32,0:19:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說別低頭了  你這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  又不知不覺了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把它放回原處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說玲子沒能完成約定是因為有特別的原因對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太瞧得起她了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一不小心忘記了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子就是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼隨便…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.03,0:20:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這書是怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是借著沒還嗎  瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看來忘了不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去真像是有特別原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  玲子啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那算是什麼啊  真莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.86,0:21:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為是好朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  昨天怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下  這個拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹田  笹田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天婦羅麵條裡的蝦  你是先吃還是後吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.41,0:21:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好朋友…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天  謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你很為難嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉入了水壩的村子出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棲身在那的妖怪們為了要回名字而來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.24,0:23:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你這傢伙  別纏住夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時要麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.91,0:23:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見的人…
